@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}

<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Escalation</h1>
    <p class="lead">Escalation is a simple web game about what actions lead to increasing or decreasing the intensity of global conflicts. </p>
    @Html.ActionLink("Start Playing", "StartNew", "GameManagement", routeValues: null, htmlAttributes: new { @class = "btn btn-primary btn-lg" })
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <i>There may be situations in which striking a center of gravity might deliver a fatal blow; but the enemy might still be able to retaliate with a lethal or unacceptably damaging response, much like a spider whose legs continue to strike after it is dead. This phenomenon is what nuclear strategist Herman Kahn once referred to as “insensate war" and it is still a possibility in today’s globalized world.</i>
    </div>
</div>